ROCKTILLYOUDROP saved ground inside early, moved up closer to the leaders in the backstretch, rallied between foes into the final turn and wilted. DRINKING AGAIN offered little. GLAVA stalked the early pace in the two path, moved up alongside IMPACTO to challenge the lead, and stopped. RACE HOME outrun throughout, was distanced and eased.
